import React from 'react';
import {Pagination,PaginationItem,PaginationLink} from 'reactstrap';

const PaginationComponent = (props) => {
    console.log(props)
    return(
        <Pagination aria-label="Page navigation example">
            
            <PaginationItem active>
                <PaginationLink onClick={()=>props.changePage(1)} href="#">
                1
                </PaginationLink>
            </PaginationItem>
            <PaginationItem>
                <PaginationLink onClick={()=>props.changePage(2)} href="#">
                2
                </PaginationLink>
            </PaginationItem>
            <PaginationItem>
                <PaginationLink onClick={()=>props.changePage(1)} href="#">
                3
                </PaginationLink>
            </PaginationItem>
            <PaginationItem>
                <PaginationLink href="#">
                4
                </PaginationLink>
            </PaginationItem>
            <PaginationItem>
                <PaginationLink href="#">
                5
                </PaginationLink>
            </PaginationItem>
            
        </Pagination>
    );
}
export default PaginationComponent;
